  "texts": [
    "These non-interactive approaches overlook the fact that the drug discovery process is actually about incorporating the experience of these experts and iteratively improving the drug through these people's judgment of whether the drug was successful or not.",
    "To address this gap, a team of scientists created DrugAssist [29], an interactive molecule optimization model that performs drug optimization through human-machine dialogue by leveraging the powerful interactivity and performance of LLMs.",
    "DrugAssist has high hopes to pave the way for future research in the LLM application of new drug discovery.",
    "The key concept here, which will be explored further on, is that humans and machines can work together to create more effective results.More progress has been happening in the past two years in the field of Multimodal LLMs which in essence is a collection of specialized LLMs that work together, for example Chat GPT-4o.",
    "It is based on multimodal architecture, and consisting of a combination of three AI models, text, audio, and vision."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "To address this gap, a team of scientists created DrugAssist [29], an interactive molecule optimization model that performs drug optimization through human-machine dialogue by leveraging the powerful interactivity and performance of LLMs."
  ]
